leading_list
['/*+Leading(ci t)*/', '/*+Leading(t cc)*/', '/*+Leading(t kt)*/']
real time: 30508.42
pg plan: 0.056277 pg run: 30.508419999999997
totalTime: 30508.42
mcts: 0.07613086700439453 plan gen: 0.056277 MPHE: 0.03405904769897461 hinter latency: 30.508419999999997
SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 2008
AND k.keyword IN ('superhero',
'computer-animated-movie',
'female-nudity',
'based-on-novel',
'second-part',
'based-on-comic',
'tv-special',
'violence',
'hospital',
'tv-special');

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('complete',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Sci-Fi',
'Action')
AND t.production_year > 2001;

     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')

                    'gore',

                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('complete',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Action',
'Horror')
AND t.production_year > 1983;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,

       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie

     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t

  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'

  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id

SQL : SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,

     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t

       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'

  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t

       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')

  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id

     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t

       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')

FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t

                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')

  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'

  AND t.id = mk.movie_id

  AND rt.id = ci.role_id

  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id

  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Home Entertainment'

'death-of-mother')
AND t.production_year > 2009;

     keyword AS k,

     movie_keyword AS mk,

     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind = 'complete'

       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')

  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id

       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('second-part',
'violence',
'gore',
'party')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '8.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND t.production_year > 1999
AND k.keyword IN ('murder-in-title',
'superhero',
'based-on-comic',
'laser');

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('cast',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Crime',
'Crime')
AND t.production_year > 2001;

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('crew',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Western',
'Horror')
AND t.production_year > 1983;

pg plan: 0.036493000000000005 pg run: 6.654528

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('character-name-in-title',
'revenge',
'fight',
'violence',
'murder',
'death',
'magnet',
'second-part',
'violence',
'murder-in-title')
AND t.production_year > 2000;

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(n.name) AS writer,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
                  '(head writer)',
                  '(written by)',
                  '(story)',
                  '(story editor)')
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'votes'
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
                    'violence',
                    'blood',
                    'gore',
                    'death',
                    'female-nudity',
                    'hospital')
  AND n.gender = 'm'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND cct1.kind IN ('crew',
'cast')
AND mi.info IN ('Thriller',
'Horror')
AND t.production_year > 1983;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_action_movie_jap_eng
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.production_year > 2010
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('fight',
'second-part',
'murder');

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('character-name-in-title',
'second-part',
'tv-special',
'hand-to-hand-combat',

'marvel-comics',
'sequel',
'laser',

'marvel-comics')
AND t.production_year > 2002;

     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,

     role_type AS rt,

                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')

  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id

     comp_cast_type AS cct2,

     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t

FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.production_year > 2010
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('second-part',
'marvel-comics',
'superhero');

     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,

     title AS t

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('sequel',
'fight',
'based-on-comic',
'marvel-comics',
'tv-special',
'sequel',
'tv-special',
'murder',
'murder',
'tv-special')
AND t.production_year > 2002;

FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,

                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')

     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,

     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,

     info_type AS it2,

     name AS n1,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE a1.person_id = n1.id

  AND cn.country_code = '[de]'

     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND ci.note like '%Rylan)%'
AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
AND rt.role = 'actress'
AND t.production_year > 2009;

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.gender IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.note IS NULL
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND ci.note IN ('(producer)',
'(writer)',
'(executive producer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(voice)')
AND mi.info IN ('Family',
'Western')
AND mi_idx.info > '10'
AND n.gender = 'm'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1997  AND 2007;

SQL : SELECT MIN(an.name) AS acress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_anime_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an.person_id = n.id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2006)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%')
  AND n.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND rt.role = 'miscellaneous crew'
AND t.title like 'Dead%'
AND ci.note = '(lead tester)'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1998  AND 2006;

['/*+Leading(ci t)*/', '/*+Leading(ci mi_idx)*/', '/*+Leading(ci n)*/']
real time: 8631.713

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.gender IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.note IS NULL
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(voice)',
'(executive producer)',
'(producer)',
'(uncredited)')
AND mi.info IN ('Drama',
'War')
AND mi_idx.info > '6.4'
AND n.gender = 'm'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2013;

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS member_in_charnamed_movie,
       MIN(n.name) AS a1
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.keyword ='character-name-in-title'

  AND ci.movie_id = t.id

  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id

'Family',

'Sci-Fi',

SQL : SELECT MIN(an.name) AS acress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_anime_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an.person_id = n.id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2006)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%')
  AND n.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND rt.role = 'miscellaneous crew'
AND t.title like 'X-Men:%'
AND ci.note = '(script supervisor: splinter unit)'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2004  AND 2012;

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.gender IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.note IS NULL
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(voice)',
'(uncredited)',
'(producer)',
'(writer)')
AND mi.info IN ('Horror',
'War')
AND mi_idx.info > '6.2'
AND n.gender = 'm'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2001;

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.gender IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.note IS NULL
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
'(producer)',
'(writer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(executive producer)')
AND mi.info IN ('Western',
'Thriller')
AND mi_idx.info > '5'
AND n.gender = 'f'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1996  AND 2012;

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.gender IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.note IS NULL
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND it1.info = 'genres'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
'(producer)',
'(writer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(executive producer)')
AND mi.info IN ('Action',
'Crime')
AND mi_idx.info > '6.6'
AND n.gender = 'm'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2009;
[['PG'], [2615.942]]

SQL : SELECT MIN(an.name) AS acress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_anime_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an.person_id = n.id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2006)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%')
  AND n.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND rt.role = 'writer'
AND t.title like 'The%'
AND ci.note = '(based on the novel by)'

SQL : SELECT MIN(an.name) AS acress_pseudonym,
       MIN(t.title) AS japanese_anime_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE an.person_id = n.id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND ci.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND ci.role_id = rt.id
  AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
  AND mc.note LIKE '%(Japan)%'
  AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%'
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2006)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%')
  AND n.name LIKE '%Yo%'
  AND n.name NOT LIKE '%Yu%'
  AND cn.country_code ='[jp]'
  AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND rt.role = 'editor'
AND t.title like 'Suspicion%'
AND ci.note = '(as Ron E. Yoshida)'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1995  AND 2004;

     info_type AS it2,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     name AS n,
     title AS t

       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Sm%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2005  AND 2013;
[['PG'], [5036.415]]
1.5346 2.3604 0.0000 0.4947 216.5434 215.1425 0.9935

     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,

     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.title = 'Shrek 2'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id

  AND t.id = cc.movie_id

  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id

  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id

FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,

pg plan: 0.06657500000000001 pg run: 6.360017
totalTime: 636758.0680000001
mcts: 0.10260772705078125 plan gen: 0.06657500000000001 MPHE: 0.023857831954956055 hinter latency: 6.360017
SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Br%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2004;

     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id

  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND n.name like '%Jo%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1999  AND 2001;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id

FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t

                  '(voice: Japanese version)',

                  '(voice: English version)')

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')

     keyword AS k,

SQL : SELECT count(*)
FROM aka_name AS an,
     complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it3,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     person_info AS pi,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind ='cast'
  AND cct2.kind ='complete+verified'
  AND chn.name = 'Queen'
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND it3.info = 'trivia'
  AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.title = 'Shrek 2'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id

  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id

  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = pi.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
  AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
